              <span id="reviewTextContainer3028522826" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3631325615036770787">Such an important read! Maya is able to show us why prisons and policing don’t produce safety while also showing us how to build up transformative practices that do. She reminds us that abolition isn’t only about tearing down harmful structures, but also about building up healing ones. This book should be in every abolitionist toolkit. <br/></span>

          </span>
