  <span id="freeText9528756084836340368" style="display:none">Incredible resources and examples to guide us on the path to a world beyond policing, incarceration, and the school-to-prison pipeline. Her writing is engaging and weaves in a beautiful narrative about her family's own relationship with incarceration.<br /><br />The author comes from an abolitionist perspective and her writing really calls you to action (and provides you with a litany of ways to get involved). This book makes you feel that transformative justice in an overly punitive society is possible if we fight for it.</span>
