<div id="review_1071094276" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1071094276" />
    <a title="Julia" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/8087575-julia"><img alt="Julia" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1443904010p2/8087575.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1071094276?book_show_action=true">Jun 22, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Julia" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Julia" href="/user/show/8087575-julia">Julia</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1071094276" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11608720633744498227">Such an insightful, well-written, engaging, and personal account of the stories of prisoners and their families, her own sister&apos;s incarceration, and the broken punitive system that we live in. Maya Schenwar leaves you feeling angry, hopeful, and ready for restorative/transformative change. This is an important book, something that everyone should read.</span>
  <span id="freeText11608720633744498227" style="display:none">Such an insightful, well-written, engaging, and personal account of the stories of prisoners and their families, her own sister's incarceration, and the broken punitive system that we live in. Maya Schenwar leaves you feeling angry, hopeful, and ready for restorative/transformative change. This is an important book, something that everyone should read.</span>
