              <span id="reviewTextContainer2417985148" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13569955995511640021">Prison is a relatively new institution in our society, and an aggressively harmful one. This covers some of that harm and how and why it works the way it does, and also addresses the prison abolition movement and restorative justice and other prison alternatives. Very well done.</span>

          </span>
