<div id="review_1869238589" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1869238589" />
    <a title="Jamie Boyd" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/63233108-jamie-boyd"><img alt="Jamie Boyd" src="https://s.gr-assets.com/assets/nophoto/user/u_50x66-632230dc9882b4352d753eedf9396530.png" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1869238589?book_show_action=true">Jan 16, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Jamie Boyd" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Jamie Boyd" href="/user/show/63233108-jamie-boyd">Jamie Boyd</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/63233108-jamie-boyd?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1869238589" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12308443552450080007">This book presents the basics of how our mass incarceration system is failing all the people whose lives are touched by it. The unflinching look at the heroin epidemic - as viewed by supportive family members - will be easy to relate to for a growing number of families.<br/><br/>This book is accessible to a broad audience but also directs interested readers to sources for more; more reading as well as more action.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


