<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17847530-dog-whistle-politics"><img alt="Dog Whistle Politics: How Coded Racial Appeals Have Reinvented Racism and Wrecked the Middle Class" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1370836680l/17847530._SX98_.jpg" />
